2%2F1484230-20191004.htm&h=9b6f7ca8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484230-20191004.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n金鐘佢地已經打到熟晒<br />\n知道晒我地有咩不足、點樣可以捉到最多人<br />\n而家已經有晒部署駐晒兵<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔好再打冇把握嘅仗，去返自己地頭，遍地開花！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"853c8782f6549830f7e6fa4c11b103ce151ebc28","tid":1619260,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"想做雞又想拎貞節牌坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}